OL,3,CHow Reeves will respond to the IMF
OL,4,Cgrowth downgrade
OL,6,FThe IMF is forecasting that the cost
OL,7,Fto the UK of US President Donald
OL,8,FTrump's Iran war will be a half
OL,9,Fpercentage point off GDP growth this
OL,10,Fyear, to a paltry 0.8%, with inflation
OL,11,Fnudging 4% and unemployment of 5.6%.
OL,13,FIt means the UK will be hurt more than
OL,14,FTrump's America and more than the
OL,15,Fother G7 rich nations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
