CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776250558
OL,3,CHow Reeves will respond to the IMF
OL,4,Cgrowth downgrade
OL,6,FAnd for the avoidance of doubt, on the
OL,7,FIMF's methodology, all these forecasts
OL,8,Fare too optimistic, because they are
OL,9,Fbased on the market prices for oil,
OL,10,Fgas and fertiliser feedstocks more
OL,11,Fthan a month ago - on March 10 - when
OL,12,Fthere was residual optimism that the
OL,13,Fconflict could be over by now.
OL,15,FSo it will be a difficult year for
OL,16,Fmost households and businesses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
