OL,3,CHow Reeves will respond to the IMF
OL,4,Cgrowth downgrade
OL,6,FThe uncertainties about when traffic
OL,7,Fof goods and energy through the strait
OL,8,Fmay resume in any size means only a
OL,9,Fmug would forecast with confidence the
OL,10,Fprecise impact on our living
OL,11,Fstandards, business conditions or tax
OL,12,Frevenues.
OL,14,FThe Chancellor does not want to be a
OL,15,Fmug. So she won't say till nearer
OL,16,FJuly, when household energy bills are
OL,17,Fnext due to increase, how much she
OL,18,Fwill subsidise those households bills
OL,19,Fand who will get the subsidy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
