OL,3,CHow Reeves will respond to the IMF
OL,4,Cgrowth downgrade
OL,6,FReeves has been clear that universal
OL,7,Fsupport, as per what Truss promised in
OL,8,Fher brief tenure as pm, is
OL,9,Funaffordable and won't be afforded.
OL,11,FShe will target support at those who
OL,12,Fare most vulnerable, due to health
OL,13,Ffrailties, and those who are on lowest
OL,14,Fincomes.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
