OL,3,CHow Reeves will respond to the IMF
OL,4,Cgrowth downgrade
OL,6,FRight now, the Treasury has an urgent
OL,7,Fproject to establish whether HMRC and
OL,8,Fthe Department of Work and Pensions
OL,9,Fcan provide her with detailed granular
OL,10,Fdata so that she can ensure only those
OL,11,Fwho most need help will receive it.
OL,13,FHer reasoning is that if she spends
OL,14,Fwhat the nation's creditors would
OL,15,Fconsider "too much," they would
OL,16,Fpenalise the government by pushing up
OL,17,Fthe interest rate it pays - which
OL,18,Fwould in turn push up rates on
OL,19,Fmortgages.
OL,26,@wD@JOUwD@TO]
